<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar.ejs') %>

<div class="container">
  <h1>About <span style="color: #d32323;"> WanderLust</span> </h1>

  <p><h2>Hello <b style="color: rgba(235, 32, 32, 0.455);">
  <%= currUser ? currUser.username : "Freshie" %>!
</b></h2>
<strong>WanderLust</strong> is a modern Airbnb-style listing platform where you can explore, add, and manage travel destinations across the world. Built for travelers and hosts alike, our mission is to make finding a stay as easy and delightful as the trip itself.</p>

  <p>Whether you want to find hidden gems, showcase your property, or just dream about where to go next — WanderLust helps you get there.</p>

  <p>This project is part of a full-stack application built using Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and EJS templating, styled with custom CSS to resemble the elegance and simplicity of Airbnb.</p>

  <div class="buttons">
    <form action="/listings/new" method="get">
      <button type="submit">Add New Listing</button>
    </form>
    <form action="/listings" method="get">
      <button type="submit">View All Listings</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>    <h1>What Our Users Felt With <span style="color: #d32323;"> WanderLust</span> </h1>

<section class="testimonials">

  <div class="testimonial">
    <div class="testimonial-img">
      <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/220?img=12" alt="User 1">
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-content">
      <h3>Alex Johnson</h3>
      <p>“WanderLust made my backpacking trip so smooth! Booking local homestays was never this easy, and every host I met was super welcoming.”</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="testimonial">
    <div class="testimonial-img">
      <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/220?img=32" alt="User 2">
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-content">
      <h3>Priya Mehra</h3>
      <p>“I listed my family cottage on WanderLust and started receiving bookings within a week! The platform is clean and user-friendly.”</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="testimonial">
    <div class="testimonial-img">
      <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/220?img=45" alt="User 3">
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-content">
      <h3>David Kim</h3>
      <p>“The UI is so elegant and reminiscent of Airbnb. It helped me discover lesser-known gems while traveling across Europe. Highly recommend it!”</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>